    "name": "Unprompted",
    "steam_appid": 2129130,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129130/extras/bed17c28b5e4e49f117182db402f244e.poster.avif?t=1770462221\" width=250 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129130/extras/bed17c28b5e4e49f117182db402f244e.webm?t=1770462221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129130/extras/bed17c28b5e4e49f117182db402f244e.mp4?t=1770462221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129130/extras/aa44020954b96e8817b75c63426d0cff.webp?t=1770462221\" width=119 height=51 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A.I. 已经到来。</strong>每一幅精心策划的作品，皆源自一条隐藏的指令。你的任务是揭晓这些指令——并在这一过程中，感受 A.I.如何解读并诠释自身的创作</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129130/extras/9e017effe0fbd004f0a906a18dd1d4c8.poster.avif?t=1770462221\" width=600 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129130/extras/9e017effe0fbd004f0a906a18dd1d4c8.webm?t=1770462221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129130/extras/9e017effe0fbd004f0a906a18dd1d4c8.mp4?t=1770462221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129130/extras/f9dee48eea76c757acf108d23541dc0b.avif?t=1770462221\" width=586 height=65 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>欢迎来到 Museum of the Unprompted！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >MoTU 邀请所有人踏上这场关于机器的学习之旅。<br>MoTU 通过游戏化的艺术体验，与观众建立互动。<br>MoTU 构建包容性的空间，让人类与机器思维相遇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >MoTU 的体验由四个核心原则引导：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129130/extras/d9962d805edc366702fc2fafb7583937.webp?t=1770462221\" width=70 height=23 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>猜测   </strong>凝神细观每一件作品，你会逐渐察觉熟悉的元素。大胆猜测，并将你想到的词语输入文本框。按下回车键即可验证是否匹配成功，每一个正确的词语都会为你赢得积分。无需顾虑，你可以尽情无限尝试；任何暂时跳过的作品，之后仍会再次出现。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129130/extras/57ee8bd51380048ac123126bd3280d63.webp?t=1770462221\" width=62 height=23 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>提示   </strong>如果你不确定自己看到的是什么，可花费 <strong>10 分</strong>来揭示提示词中的一个词。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129130/extras/a8b9580c6794176e44c19b6d23f89f10.webp?t=1770462221\" width=60 height=23 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129130/extras/55aeaa5aa462bec4b61f585d85b488b9.poster.avif?t=1770462221\" width=80 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129130/extras/55aeaa5aa462bec4b61f585d85b488b9.webm?t=1770462221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129130/extras/55aeaa5aa462bec4b61f585d85b488b9.mp4?t=1770462221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129130/extras/642281dcea9ac3fcc4474a9c8c98ace7.poster.avif?t=1770462221\" width=80 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129130/extras/642281dcea9ac3fcc4474a9c8c98ace7.webm?t=1770462221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129130/extras/642281dcea9ac3fcc4474a9c8c98ace7.mp4?t=1770462221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129130/extras/72ea73da2c68a95cd6ba4f0a81993c40.poster.avif?t=1770462221\" width=80 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129130/extras/72ea73da2c68a95cd6ba4f0a81993c40.webm?t=1770462221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129130/extras/72ea73da2c68a95cd6ba4f0a81993c40.mp4?t=1770462221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129130/extras/a6312ce8c26491ba3af0559ff42d102c.poster.avif?t=1770462221\" width=80 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129130/extras/a6312ce8c26491ba3af0559ff42d102c.webm?t=1770462221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129130/extras/a6312ce8c26491ba3af0559ff42d102c.mp4?t=1770462221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>礼品   </strong>你在完成提示词过程中取得的进度，将使你有机会在礼品店解锁专属纪念品。在那里，AI画作将在各类商品上焕发生机，千万不要错过！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129130/extras/8c2f9b6e9ca99be74c5c1bc0a39f0e78.webp?t=1770462221\" width=142 height=23 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>互动   </strong>破解特定艺术品的提示词后，将触发由 A.I. 生成的对该作品的文本阐释，让你有机会领略机器学习联想的奇妙世界。在每次开始参观新展厅时，你还会看到由 A.I. 生成的、关于人工智能在艺术与社会中未来角色的更宏观陈述。这些内容将逐步构建起一条背景叙事，随着你探索的深入，悄然重塑你对眼前作品的认知。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129130/extras/f65bccb38bf342d877b24b6b2a319dbd.poster.avif?t=1770462221\" width=600 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129130/extras/f65bccb38bf342d877b24b6b2a319dbd.webm?t=1770462221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129130/extras/f65bccb38bf342d877b24b6b2a319dbd.mp4?t=1770462221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>来自 2026 年的一则说明</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unprompted</strong> 创作于 2022 年初，那时生成式人工智能尚属新生事物，并且在视觉上显得怪异而粗糙。在随后的几年里，A.I. 生成的图像变得愈发精致 —— 同时也引发了更多争议。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这款游戏从未试图取代艺术家，也无意为创造性工作寻找捷径。它是一次围绕机器生成内容的游戏设计实验：我想探讨的是，当机器的角色被强调而非隐藏时，会催生出怎样的游戏体验、思考与好奇心。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在无意之间，<strong>Unprompted</strong> 已经成为一枚时间胶囊——记录了我们与人工智能尚处初期的某个时刻：那时技术的局限性仍然清晰可见，其产出也更显异样和陌生。如今，它为我们打开了一扇通往那个时刻的小窗——提醒着我们，这项技术曾经以何种面貌出现在我们眼前。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >---</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unprompted</strong> 由 <strong>Matt Eshleman</strong> 创作。该项目的灵感诞生于 2022 年春季上海的新冠封控期间。当时他被封控在公寓中长达两个月，期间持续进行着实验性游戏创作。正是在这段特殊时期，Matt 对即将到来的人工智能时代，既产生了深切的忧虑，也开始尝试谨慎地拥抱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unprompted</strong> 既非完全由人类创作，也非完全由 A.I. 生成。因此，设计者对本游戏的全部内容承担最终责任。游戏中使用的图像由 <strong>Craiyon</strong> 生成。部分文本借助OpenAI的大规模语言生成模型（<strong>ChatGPT</strong>与<strong>GPT-3</strong>）辅助创作。所有由AI生成的文本草稿均经过开发者审阅与修改，以确保其符合创作意图。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>说明：</strong> 游戏界面目前仅提供英文版本。玩家需具备一定的英语词汇和短语基础，以便进行 <strong>Unprompted</strong> 的游玩。</p>",
